      <h2 class="column">Why AstroPay?</h2>
      <p>Unless you accept local payment methods, your conversion rates in Brazil will be minimal. AstroPay helps you raise your conversion rates with a first-class payment solution. AstroPay already processes huge amounts for internet companies and can even be a merchant of record if required. </p>
      <a class="btn" href="why-astropay.html">Read more »</a> </div>
