      <ul>
        <li>No need to set up a Brazilian subsidiary.</li>
        <li> Customers use their favourite payment methods (Boleto, On Line Bank Payments, Debit Cards) and pay in local currency.</li>
        <li> You are paid in USD, EUR or GBP anywhere in the world via wire transfer. </li>
      </ul>
      <a class="btn" href="why-astropay.html">Read more »</a> </div>
